{"tid":414864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封呀封呀快啲封】WhatsApp內地再被封鎖 大陸網民：我要爆炸了","createTime":"2017-09-26T13:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T14:27:42.000Z","uid":7222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4044ed1fe55aca2d4f508446afc10f0da171e7cd","tid":414864,"uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:59:54.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp內地再被封鎖 大陸網民：害我聯系不上客戶我要爆炸了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即時通訊應用程式WhatsApp晚上在內地又被封鎖！大陸網民晚上議論紛紛，指WhatsApp不能收發訊息、發相發片，甚至發語音都無法傳送，需翻牆才可以登入，很多在內地居住的港人和外國人都感到不便。不過，使用香港漫遊卡服務及在香港登記電話的用戶就暫不受影響，有網友相信，今次官方再加強對社群平台的管控，與10月18日中共召開第十九次全國代表大會有關。<br />\n<br />\n據知，今次WhatsApp在內地被封鎖由昨天開始，有部份巿民昨晨9時開始已出現短暫「失聯」問題，但至今完全無法登入。大陸網民紛紛在網上論壇發帖「今天你們的WhatsApp能用嗎？」、「一直顯示連接中，換手機也不行」、「WhatsApp發不出消息了？」、「WhatsApp在國內不能用嗎？」、「害我聯系不上客戶我要爆炸了」。<br />\n<br />\n有在大陸居住的港人表示，這次比7月和8月時的監控力度似乎更強了，「之後都間歇性用到的，現在是完全癱瘓了！」《蘋果》記者接到讀者反映後，晚上與身在內地的港人實測，發現用中國電話登記的用戶完全被封死，無法發出及接受收文字訊息，甚至圖片、影片、語音都無法載入及發送。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170925/57255591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170925%2F57255591&d=ZP7SNDWUMIiicflaSKQl3jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=140b0741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170925%2F57255591&h=88d0d1be\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170925/57255591</a>"},{"pid":"81d1d91e6813f5b1709466052f1938676e0d0bc2","tid":414864,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"咁愛國，用咩WhatsApp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee07f2d9f689a7f4c7db337f0f049c85b1e7b816","tid":414864,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d580663bf8516aa663a0ac4da57d5d40dd71ccac","tid":414864,"uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:07:52.000Z","msg":"「在大陸居住的港人」<br />\n<br />\n抵死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a98ce6c76b402bf51da859d88cbc697738930e8","tid":414864,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:27:42.000Z","msg":"封哂佢就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}